## S 5. Write Top-Level Comment (3 evaluates total)

Comment box already visible on post page (no reply click needed).

⚠️ **Some posts use plain `<textarea>` instead of TipTap.** If `.tiptap.ProseMirror` not found, fall back to `textarea.value = window.__data.text` + input event.

🚨 **Two-step pattern** — TipTap needs an event loop tick before submit button enables.
- ❌ **NEVER** combine text insertion + submit check in ONE evaluate — `submitBtn.disabled` will be `true`
- ❌ **NEVER** add `.click()` on submit in the same evaluate as `execCommand('insertText')`
- ✅ Step 1 = insert text ONLY. Step 2 = wait + submit. Step 3 = wait + verify.

```bash
# Step 1 of 3: Insert text ONLY (no submit attempt!)
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { var commentBox = document.querySelector('.comment-box'); if (!commentBox) return { error: 'comment_box_not_found' }; var editor = commentBox.querySelector('.tiptap.ProseMirror'); if (!editor) return { error: 'editor_not_found' }; editor.focus(); document.execCommand('selectAll', false, null); document.execCommand('delete', false, null); document.execCommand('insertText', false, window.__data.text); editor.dispatchEvent(new InputEvent('input', { data: window.__data.text, inputType: 'insertText', bubbles: true })); return { inserted: true, textLen: editor.innerText.length }; }", "data": {"text": "YOUR_COMMENT_HERE"}}
ENDJSON
```

```bash
# Step 2 of 3: Wait 500ms for TipTap state propagation, then submit
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 500)); var commentBox = document.querySelector('.comment-box'); if (!commentBox) return { error: 'comment_box_not_found' }; var submitBtn = commentBox.querySelector('.comment-box__save-button'); if (!submitBtn) return { error: 'submit_button_not_found' }; if (submitBtn.disabled) return { error: 'submit_still_disabled' }; submitBtn.click(); return { success: true }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

```bash
# Step 3 of 3: Wait 3s, verify OUR comment posted
# 🚨 Use "{{handle}}" (username shown on page), NOT "{{name}}" (full name — NOT rendered)
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000)); var comments = document.querySelectorAll('.comment'); var ourCount = 0; comments.forEach(function(c) { if (c.innerText.indexOf('{{handle}}') >= 0) ourCount++; }); return { verified: ourCount > 0, commentCount: comments.length, ourComments: ourCount }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

🚨 **Retry rules (STRICT — do NOT deviate):**
- If `verified: true`: success, proceed to tracking.
- If `ourComments > 1`: duplicate was posted — do NOT retry, log `Type="Error:DuplicateComment"`, proceed to tracking.
- If `verified: false` AND `ourComments == 0` AND `commentCount` UNCHANGED from before step 1: retry step 2 ONLY (click submit). **NEVER re-insert text.** If retry also fails: HEARTBEAT_BLOCKED.
- If `verified: false` AND `commentCount` INCREASED: comment likely posted — treat as success, proceed to tracking.
- ❌ **NEVER re-insert text and re-submit as a "fix"** — this is the #1 cause of duplicate comments.

## S 6. Upvote Post (single evaluate — click + wait + verify)

```bash
# 1 evaluate: upvote + 1s wait + verify (NOT 3 separate steps)
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { var postUpvote = document.querySelector('.post-liker'); if (!postUpvote) return { error: 'upvote_button_not_found' }; if (postUpvote.classList.contains('post-liker--liked')) return { skipped: true, reason: 'already_upvoted' }; postUpvote.click(); await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000)); var verified = document.querySelector('.post-liker--liked') !== null; return { success: true, verified: verified }; }"}
ENDJSON
```
